      <title>多米尼加连任总统，经济强劲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-20/dominican-president-abinader-wins-second-term-as-rivals-concede</link>
      <description><![CDATA[多米尼加共和国的亲商总统路易斯·阿比纳德在周日的选举中在第一轮选举中以压倒性优势获胜，选民奖励他成为美洲最强大的经济体之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-20/dominican-president-abinader-wins-second-term-as-rivals-concede</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 02:26:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度大选孟买投票，反对派势力增强</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-20/mumbai-heads-to-polls-in-phase-five-of-india-s-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度金融首都孟买的选民——这里是亿万富翁、电影明星和数百万贫民窟居民的家园——周一进行了投票，反对派联盟再次推动打破总理纳伦德拉·莫迪的权力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-20/mumbai-heads-to-polls-in-phase-five-of-india-s-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
